[13/07/2019 09:26:37] <font color="#0000ff">Dignifica sus...</font>
[13/07/2019 09:26:40] <font color="#0000ff">almas.</font>
[13/07/2019 09:26:43] <font color="#0000ff">Dignifica sus...</font>
[13/07/2019 09:26:47] <font color="#0000ff">almas.</font>
[13/07/2019 09:26:53] <font color="#0000ff">Para que se reconcilien contigo.</font>
[13/07/2019 09:26:59] <font color="#0000ff">Y se amiguen conmigo.</font>
[13/07/2019 09:27:06] <font color="#0000ff">Según tu voluntad.</font>
